|-
|align=right|'''[[城巴90B線|90B]]'''||align=center|{{HK Bus Route HKIsland|90B|inline}}||<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/routes/routeinfo.aspx?intLangID=2&searchtype=1&routenumber=90&route=90B&routetype=D&company=5 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-06-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304134209/http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/routes/routeinfo.aspx?intLangID=2&searchtype=1&routenumber=90&route=90B&routetype=D&company=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
|-
|align=right|'''[[城巴90C線|90C]]'''||align=center|{{HK Bus Route HKIsland|90C|inline}}||<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/routes/routeinfo.aspx?intLangID=2&searchtype=1&routenumber=90&route=90C&routetype=M&company=5 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-06-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133127/http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/routes/routeinfo.aspx?intLangID=2&searchtype=1&routenumber=90&route=90C&routetype=M&company=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
|-
|align=right|'''[[城巴N90線|N90]]'''||align=center|{{HK Bus Route HKIsland|N90|inline}}||<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/routes/routeinfo.aspx?intLangID=2&searchtype=1&routenumber=90&route=N90&routetype=N&company=5 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-06-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304122346/http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/routes/routeinfo.aspx?intLangID=2&searchtype=1&routenumber=90&route=N90&routetype=N&company=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
